transArray.content: Wow! The simple words of the little master, the moment I saw the good comments, I was moved, because your affirmation is the greatest support and encouragement for us. Your praise is a beacon for us, always guiding us to move forward to higher standards. We constantly correct ourselves and improve ourselves. This is also a blessing to our lovely customers----you-- -Maximum return. The store has added a self-service laundry room and a high-temperature sterilization dryer to make your journey safer and more convenient. We will always remember your support for us, and hope you will also remember that there is an expectant who is always looking forward to your visit again!
